@startuml sequence-diagram-sso
!theme plain

title Diagrama de Secuencia - Flujo SSO Completo\nHub Client Portal → Workspace / Desktop / Vista

actor "Hub Client\n(Browser)" as HubUser
participant "Hub Portal\n(React + Vite)" as HubFE
participant "API Gateway\n(Nginx)" as Gateway
participant "Django REST\nBackend" as API
participant "JWT Auth\nMiddleware" as JWTAuth
participant "Destination\nService\n(Workspace/Desktop)" as DestService
database "PostgreSQL" as DB
database "Redis\n(Cache)" as Redis

== 1. Generación del SSO Token ==

HubUser -> HubFE : Click "Abrir Workspace"
HubFE -> Gateway : POST /api/v1/auth/sso/token/\n{service: "workspace"}\nAuthorization: Bearer {hub_access_token}
Gateway -> JWTAuth : Forward request
JWTAuth -> JWTAuth : Decode & validate JWT\n(firma, expiración, tenant_id)

alt JWT inválido o expirado
  JWTAuth --> HubUser : 401 Unauthorized\n{error: "Token expired, please login"}
end

JWTAuth -> API : request + user context

API -> DB : SELECT TenantService\nWHERE tenant_id = ? AND service = 'workspace'\nAND status = 'active'

alt Servicio no adquirido o suspendido
  API --> HubUser : 403 Forbidden\n{error: "Service not available for your plan"}
end

alt Servicio no existe
  API --> HubUser : 404 Not Found\n{error: "Service not found"}
end

API -> API : Generar token = secrets.token_hex(32)\n(64 chars, opaco, NO JWT)
API -> DB : INSERT SSOToken {\n  user_id, tenant_id,\n  service: "workspace",\n  token: hex_token,\n  expires_at: now() + 60s,\n  used_at: NULL\n}
API -> DB : INSERT AuditLog\n{action: "sso.token_created",\n resource_type: "SSOToken",\n ip_address, user_agent}

note right of API
  token NUNCA se loguea en texto plano.
  Solo se audita su creación y uso.
  TTL: 60 segundos estrictos.
end note

API --> HubFE : 200 OK {\n  sso_token: "a3f9...",\n  redirect_url: "https://acme.workspace.app/auth/sso",\n  expires_in: 60\n}

HubFE -> HubUser : Redirect browser\nhttps://acme.workspace.app/auth/sso?sso_token=a3f9...

== 2. Validación del SSO Token ==

HubUser -> DestService : GET /auth/sso?sso_token=a3f9...\n(browser redirect)
DestService -> Gateway : POST /api/v1/auth/sso/validate/\n{sso_token: "a3f9..."}\n(server-to-server, no CORS)
Gateway -> API : Forward request (sin JWT de usuario)

API -> DB : SELECT SSOToken\nWHERE token = ? FOR UPDATE

alt Token no encontrado
  API --> DestService : 404 Not Found\n{error: "Invalid SSO token"}
  DestService --> HubUser : Error page: "Enlace inválido"
end

alt Token ya utilizado (used_at IS NOT NULL)
  API --> DestService : 410 Gone\n{error: "SSO token already used"}
  DestService --> HubUser : Error page: "Enlace ya utilizado.\nVuelve al Hub para obtener uno nuevo."
end

alt Token expirado (expires_at < now())
  API -> DB : DELETE SSOToken (limpieza)
  API --> DestService : 410 Gone\n{error: "SSO token expired"}
  DestService --> HubUser : Error page: "Enlace expirado (>60s).\nVuelve al Hub e intenta de nuevo."
end

' Token válido — happy path
API -> DB : UPDATE SSOToken\nSET used_at = now()\nWHERE token = ? AND used_at IS NULL\n(atomic — previene race condition)

API -> DB : SELECT User, Tenant\nWHERE user_id = ssotoken.user_id

API -> API : Generar JWT para el servicio destino\n(access_token 15min, refresh_token 7d)
note right of API
  Access Token payload:
  {user_id, tenant_id,
   roles, permissions,
   service: "workspace"}

  Refresh Token payload:
  {jti, user_id, tenant_id,
   service: "workspace"}
end note

API -> Redis : SET refresh:{jti} = user_id\nEX 604800
API -> DB : UPDATE User SET last_login = now()
API -> DB : INSERT AuditLog\n{action: "sso.token_validated",\n resource_type: "SSOToken",\n resource_id: token_id}

API --> DestService : 200 OK {\n  access_token,\n  refresh_token,\n  user: {id, name, email, roles, permissions}\n}

DestService -> DestService : Almacenar tokens\nen localStorage / cookie httpOnly
DestService --> HubUser : 302 Redirect → /dashboard\n(autenticado en Workspace)

== 3. Limpieza Periódica de Tokens Expirados ==

participant "Celery Beat\n(Scheduler)" as CeleryBeat
participant "Celery Worker" as CeleryWorker

CeleryBeat -> CeleryWorker : Trigger: cleanup_expired_sso_tokens\n(cada 5 minutos)
CeleryWorker -> DB : DELETE FROM sso_tokens\nWHERE expires_at < now()\nAND used_at IS NULL\n(tokens expirados sin usar)
DB --> CeleryWorker : N rows deleted
CeleryWorker -> DB : DELETE FROM sso_tokens\nWHERE used_at < now() - INTERVAL '1 hour'\n(tokens ya usados, antigüedad >1h)
DB --> CeleryWorker : M rows deleted

note right of CeleryWorker
  Tokens usados se conservan 1h
  para auditoría. Luego se purgan.
  Tokens expirados sin usar se
  eliminan inmediatamente.
end note

@enduml
